Package: metagene2
Version: 0.99.5
Date: 2019-04-05
Title: A package to produce metagene plots
Author: Eric Fournier <fournier.eric.2@crchudequebec.ulaval.ca>, 
    Charles Joly Beauparlant <charles.joly-beauparlant@crchul.ulaval.ca>,
